'''凱莉安·伊莉莎白·康威'''（{{lang-en|Kellyanne Elizabeth Conway}}，[[娘家|娘家]]姓氏為'''菲茨帕特里克'''〔Fitzpatrick〕；{{bd|1967年|1月20日}}），美國共和黨籍競選經理、戰略家與民意測驗專家。她是The Polling Company / Woman Trend公司的總裁兼執行長，並曾任[[CNN|CNN]]、[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞]]與[[福斯財經網|福斯財經]]等頻道節目的固定政治評論員。康威亦曾作客《[[早安美國|早安美國]]》、《[[马赫脱口秀|-{zh-hk:馬艾; zh-tw:馬厄; zh-cn:马赫;}-脫口秀]]》、《[[與媒體見面|與媒體見面]]》與《{{tsl|en|Hannity|漢尼提}}》等節目。

2016年8月17日起，康威擔任共和黨參選人[[唐納德·川普|唐納德·川普]]的競選經理<ref>{{cite news|last1=Parker|first1=Ashley|last2=Haberman|first2=Maggie|title=Donald Trump, in Shake-Up, Hires Breitbart Executive for Top Campaign Post|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/18/us/politics/donald-trump-stephen-bannon-paul-manafort.html|accessdate=17 August 2016|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=17 August 2016|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122002840/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/18/us/politics/donald-trump-stephen-bannon-paul-manafort.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。且由於川普在2016年11月8日總統大選中獲勝，讓康威成為美國史上第一位操盤總統選戰致勝的女性<ref>{{cite news |last=Lange |first=Jeva |date=November 9, 2016 |title=Kellyanne Conway becomes first woman to successfully run a presidential campaign |url=http://theweek.com/speedreads/660809/kellyanne-conway-becomes-first-woman-successfully-run-presidential-campaign |newspaper=The Week |location=[[New_York|New York]] |access-date=November 9, 2016 |quote=Hillary Clinton may not have been elected president, but other glass ceilings were shattered on Election Day nonetheless. One such historic moment came from Trump's own camp, where Kellyanne Conway became the first woman to successfully run a presidential campaign. |archive-date=2018-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925115400/http://theweek.com/speedreads/660809/kellyanne-conway-becomes-first-woman-successfully-run-presidential-campaign |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月22日，被指定為總統顧問。

自从川普就职后，康威就陷于一系列争议事件中，包括编造“{{le|鲍灵格林大屠杀|Bowling Green massacre}}”（Bowling Green massacre）以证明自己的论点，以及公开推销与总统的女儿[[伊万卡·川普|伊万卡·川普]]相关的商品。因此，许多媒体渠道质疑她的可信度，其中一些拒绝了她一对一采访的请求。<ref>Rosen, Ben. "[http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Politics/2017/0215/As-Kellyanne-Conway-s-credibility-wanes-what-should-TV-news-shows-do-video As Kellyanne Conway's credibility wanes, what should TV news shows do?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Politics/2017/0215/As-Kellyanne-Conway-s-credibility-wanes-what-should-TV-news-shows-do-video |date=20170326115420 }}". ''[[Christian_Science_Monitor|Christian Science Monitor]]'', February 15, 2017. Retrieved February 18, 2017.</ref><ref>Friedman, Megan. "[http://www.marieclaire.com/politics/news/a25449/kellyanne-conway-morning-joe-msnbc-ban/ Kellyanne Conway Has Been Banned From Appearing on the MSNBC's 'Morning Joe'. Mika Brzezinski put a stop to the madness] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marieclaire.com/politics/news/a25449/kellyanne-conway-morning-joe-msnbc-ban/ |date=20170310032324 }}. ''[[Marie_Claire|Marie Claire]]'', February 16, 2017. Retrieved February 18, 2017.</ref>

2020年8月23日，康威宣佈月底她將辭去總統顧問一職<ref>{{cite news |title=白宫顾问康威突然宣布辞职 |url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20200824-1079338 |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2020-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824110659/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20200824-1079338 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/08/claudia-conway-reacts-on-tiktok-as-kellyanne-conway-resigns.html|title=Claudia Conway Reacts on TikTok After Mom Kellyanne Announces Resignation|first=Halle|last=Kiefer|date=August 24, 2020|website=Vulture|accessdate=2020-08-24|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824140333/https://www.vulture.com/2020/08/claudia-conway-reacts-on-tiktok-as-kellyanne-conway-resigns.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53885239|title=Kellyanne Conway resigns as White House adviser|date=August 24, 2020|via=www.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2020-08-24|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824094236/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53885239|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
== 早年生活與求學 ==
凱莉安·伊莉莎白·費斯柏德列，1967年1月20日出生於紐澤西州的肯頓<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kopan|first1=Tal|title=Trump campaign manager: Obama was born in US|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/09/09/politics/kellyanne-conway-donald-trump-birtherism/index.html|work=CNN|date=September 9, 2016|accessdate=2016-10-24|archive-date=2016-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019071625/http://www.cnn.com/2016/09/09/politics/kellyanne-conway-donald-trump-birtherism/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。「康威愛爾蘭裔的父親經營一家小型托運公司，義大利裔的母親則是在銀行工作。兩人在康威3歲時離異」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsmax.com/RonaldKessler/kellyanne-conway/2008/09/22/id/325476/ |title=GOP Strategist: McCain Will Win |last1=Kessler |first1=Ronald |date=September 22, 2008 |publisher=[[Newsmax|Newsmax]] |access-date=August 17, 2016 |quote= |archive-date=2016-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022043621/http://www.newsmax.com/RonaldKessler/kellyanne-conway/2008/09/22/id/325476/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。康威在{{tsl|en|Hammonton, New Jersey|哈蒙頓 (紐澤西州)|哈蒙頓}}長大，並畢業於{{tsl|en|St. Joseph High School (Hammonton, New Jersey)|聖若瑟高級中學 (紐澤西州)|聖若瑟高級中學}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Johnson|first1=Brent|title=Meet the N.J. native who's running Donald Trump's campaign|url=http://www.nj.com/politics/index.ssf/2016/09/meet_the_nj_native_whos_running_donald_trumps_camp.html|work=NJ.com|date=September 26, 2016|accessdate=2016-10-24|archive-date=2016-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024151625/http://www.nj.com/politics/index.ssf/2016/09/meet_the_nj_native_whos_running_donald_trumps_camp.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在踏入政壇前，康威曾擔任過律師。1989年，康威於{{tsl|en|Trinity Washington University|華盛頓三一大學|華盛頓三一學院}}（現易名為{{tsl|en|Trinity Washington University|華盛頓三一大學}}）取得學士學位後，在1992年於[[喬治華盛頓大學法學院|喬治華盛頓大學法學院]]取得[[法律博士|法律博士]]學位，並在華盛頓特區擔任法官助理。康威還在華盛頓大學法學院當過4年的兼職教授<ref name=conwaybio>{{cite web|url=http://pollingcompany.com/about/kellyanne/|title=Kellyanne Conway biography|publisher=pollingcompany.com|accessdate=2016-08-22|author=The Polling Company|date=2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430223824/http://pollingcompany.com/about/kellyanne/|archivedate=2016-04-30}}</ref><ref name="ballotpedia2016">Ballotpedia (2016). Kellyanne Conway. [https://ballotpedia.org/Kellyanne_Conway Ballotpedia article on Kellyanne Conway] {{Wayback|url=https://ballotpedia.org/Kellyanne_Conway |date=20170327131635 }}.</ref>。

